                        <interp inst="t18350302-787-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 16.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy</hi>.—
<rs id="t18350302-787-punishment-92" type="punishmentDescription">
